00:13:09.471 --> 00:13:12.210
Carnot engine.
The logic is pretty simple.

00:13:12.210 --> 00:13:14.218
These numbers picked are
representative,

00:13:14.218 --> 00:13:17.359
but you can take any number as
long as your engine does better

00:13:17.359 --> 00:13:20.274
