instead of 40 calories,

00:13:20.274 --> 00:13:23.710
would have made 30 calories
needed.

00:13:23.710 --> 00:13:26.006
If it produced 30,
I'll get an engine which is

00:13:26.006 --> 00:13:28.659
one-half times as bigger than
the standard engine;

00:13:28.659 --> 00:13:31.105
run it backwards,
your 30 will feed my engine and

00:13:31.105 --> 00:13:34.316
you will find once again heat is
flowing from a cold body to hot

00:13:34.316 --> 00:13:37.169
