anywhere in the universe,

00:13:37.169 --> 00:13:40.240
that is forbidden by the
postulate.

00:13:40.240 --> 00:13:44.778
So, this is how Carnot's
engine, even though it's a very

00:13:44.778 --> 00:13:48.079
primitive engine,
is the standard for all

00:13:48.079 --> 00:13:50.261
engines.
No engine can be better than

00:13:50.261 --> 00:13:52.276
the Carnot engine.
Now, the key to the Carnot

00:13:52.276 --> 00:13:54.179
engine is that it's a reversible
engine.

00:13:54.179 --> 00:13:57.102
If I had more time I could show
