I said many things are

00:14:29.076 --> 00:14:32.149
forbidden and there is a law
that's going to forbid all of

00:14:32.149 --> 00:14:34.090
them, so I am coming to that
law.

00:14:34.090 --> 00:14:37.480
But it all started with a
person asking a very practical

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:40.070
question, "How good can I make
engines?"

00:14:40.070 --> 00:14:43.983
And what Carnot is telling you
is the best efficiency any

00:14:43.983 --> 00:14:48.387
