00:32:39.955 --> 00:32:41.420
T_0 over
T_1,

00:32:41.420 --> 00:32:44.263
the next log is log of
T_1 over

00:32:44.263 --> 00:32:47.348
T_0,
log A plus log B

00:32:47.348 --> 00:32:50.156
is log of AB.
But when you do this look what

00:32:50.156 --> 00:32:52.941
happens here.
This all cancels,

00:32:52.941 --> 00:32:56.386
log of 1 is zero;
the total entropy change is

00:32:56.386 --> 00:32:58.720
R log T_1 over
T_0.

00:33:02.609 --> 00:33:07.448
But for a gas at constant
