The correct way to do this for

00:33:39.784 --> 00:33:41.770
me would be to write
T_0 over

00:33:41.770 --> 00:33:44.022
T_1 times
T_2 over

00:33:44.022 --> 00:33:46.746
T_0,
then realize the fact that

00:33:46.746 --> 00:33:50.020
T_2 and
T_1 are equal

00:33:50.020 --> 00:33:53.250
because I am on an isotherm.
