00:33:55.554 --> 00:33:57.197
T_1,
but here T_2

00:33:57.197 --> 00:33:58.637
over T_0 is
V_2 over

00:33:58.637 --> 00:34:00.170
V_0,
which is V_2

00:34:00.170 --> 00:34:02.226
over V_1.
That's, of course,

00:34:02.226 --> 00:34:05.180
the entropy change I got in one
shot here.

00:34:05.180 --> 00:34:07.809
So, you can find entropy change
