00:34:28.454 --> 00:34:31.609
because ∆Q is positive
for heating and you divide by

00:34:31.609 --> 00:34:33.475
T,
and you make it a logarithm,

00:34:33.475 --> 00:34:35.548
but we know at every
infinitesimal portion we're

00:34:35.548 --> 00:34:38.310
adding positive numbers.
And when I cooled things it

00:34:38.310 --> 00:34:40.040
goes down.
Why not just call it

00:34:40.040 --> 00:34:41.909
