Why do you need this new

00:34:41.909 --> 00:34:44.493
concept called entropy?
So, that's what the rest of the

00:34:44.493 --> 00:34:45.991
lecture is about.
It's a very,

00:34:45.991 --> 00:34:49.179
very powerful and beautiful
concept so I wanted to explain

00:34:49.179 --> 00:34:54.374
it, make sure I get it right.
Here is now the result for all

00:34:54.374 --> 00:34:58.493
this hard work.
Remember I told you there are

