00:42:50.524 --> 00:42:53.360
will be T_1^(2) +
T_2^(2) +

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:55.500
2T_1T
_2.

00:42:55.500 --> 00:42:58.163
When I bring this guy to the
other side, it'll become minus

00:42:58.163 --> 00:43:00.275
2T_1T
_2 and so it's

00:43:00.275 --> 00:43:04.264
clearly positive.
So, when hot and cold meet and

00:43:04.264 --> 00:43:08.600
create lukewarm,
entropy of the universe has

00:43:08.600 --> 00:43:11.098
gone up.
It follows, therefore,

00:43:11.098 --> 00:43:14.442
if lukewarm spontaneously
separated into hot and cold,

00:43:14.442 --> 00:43:18.480
the entropy would go down and
that's why that doesn't happen.

00:43:18.480 --> 00:43:21.202
That's why if you leave a jar
of water at one temperature,

00:43:21.202 --> 00:43:23.637
it doesn't spontaneously
separate into a part on top

00:43:23.637 --> 00:43:25.500
which is cold and a part on
bottom,

00:43:25.500 --> 00:43:27.867
which is hot.
Such a separation would not

00:43:27.867 --> 00:43:30.775
violate anything.
It would not violate the Law of

00:43:30.775 --> 00:43:33.993
Conservation of Energy,
but it will violate the law

00:43:33.993 --> 00:43:36.309
that entropy has to always go
up.

00:43:36.309 --> 00:43:38.840
So, one way is allowed another
way is not allowed.

00:43:38.840 --> 00:43:41.800
So, you see over and over
again, that anything that's

00:43:41.800 --> 00:43:44.760
allowed is in the direction of
increasing entropy;

00:43:44.760 --> 00:43:47.966
anything that is forbidden is
in the direction of decreasing

00:43:47.966 --> 00:43:51.510
entropy.
But who is this entropy?

00:43:51.510 --> 00:43:53.806
What does it mean?
Well, that we have not

00:43:53.806 --> 00:43:56.230
understood at all from any of
these calculations.

00:43:56.230 --> 00:43:59.374
Because dQ over T
doesn't speak to us the way

00:43:59.374 --> 00:44:01.760
dU or dQ or
PdV does.

00:44:01.760 --> 00:44:07.491
So, that last part of what I'm
going to do is going to explain

00:44:07.491 --> 00:44:12.190
to you what is the microscopic
basis of entropy.

00:44:12.190 --> 00:44:16.465
Why is the entropy going up?
Why is--why do we understand

00:44:16.465 --> 00:44:21.969
the tendency of things to go the
direction of increasing entropy?

00:44:21.969 --> 00:44:25.759
All I've shown you now is that
it's a mystical quantity called

00:44:25.759 --> 00:44:29.300
entropy, circumstantially you
find every time something is

00:44:29.300 --> 00:44:31.882
forbidden,
it's because had it taken place

00:44:31.882 --> 00:44:34.929
entropy would have gone down.
Do you remember the examples?

00:44:34.929 --> 00:44:38.088
Heat flowing from hot to cold
entropy goes up,

00:44:38.088 --> 00:44:40.395
allowed.
Flowing from cold to hot,

00:44:40.395 --> 00:44:42.449
entropy goes down,
not allowed.

00:44:42.449 --> 00:44:45.190
Hot and cold mix and become
lukewarm;

00:44:45.190 --> 00:44:48.982
allowed, entropy goes up.
Luke warm separates into hot

00:44:48.982 --> 00:44:51.630
and cold;
not allowed, entropy goes down.

00:44:51.630 --> 00:44:53.489
So, there's definitely a
correlation.

00:44:53.489 --> 00:44:55.730
And yet we don't know what it
means.

00:44:55.730 --> 00:44:57.800
So, we're going to talk about
what it means.

00:44:57.800 --> 00:45:01.389
For that, I'm going to consider
