00:45:01.389 --> 00:45:08.703
I take a gas and I put it in a
room in a box where there's a

00:45:08.703 --> 00:45:13.394
partition, half way.
The molecules are stuck on the

00:45:13.394 --> 00:45:17.060
left side, gas has reached
equilibrium and it's done what

00:45:17.060 --> 00:45:20.400
it can, which is to spread out
over this volume.

00:45:20.400 --> 00:45:23.370
Now, I suddenly remove the
