00:46:58.760 --> 00:47:01.630
you can do what you want,
so this entropy change is zero.

00:47:01.630 --> 00:47:03.090
But that is a wrong argument.

00:47:06.099 --> 00:47:08.902
Can you think about why that's
not the way to do the entropy

00:47:08.902 --> 00:47:11.040
change?
Why that's the wrong analysis?

00:47:15.460 --> 00:47:17.560
First of all,
could that be the right answer?

00:47:17.560 --> 00:47:21.246
Yes.
Student: It can't

00:47:21.246 --> 00:47:25.347
because then that would mean
