00:48:04.350 --> 00:48:09.059
Any views on this?
Yep.

00:48:09.059 --> 00:48:12.572
Student: [inaudible]
Professor Ramamurti

00:48:12.572 --> 00:48:15.869
Shankar: Ah,
well, you can say it is cooler

00:48:15.869 --> 00:48:18.880
