00:48:22.782 --> 00:48:25.516
pressure, right?
If, when--If I were to move

00:48:25.516 --> 00:48:27.943
this piston here,
there is no pressure pushing

00:48:27.943 --> 00:48:30.150
this gas back.
Do you understand that?

00:48:30.150 --> 00:48:33.920
Doesn't do any work,
