00:48:33.920 --> 00:48:37.426
So, what does that mean?
In the end when you settle

00:48:37.426 --> 00:48:40.433
down, what can you conclude?
No heat input,

00:48:40.433 --> 00:48:43.901
no work done,
so what does that mean in terms

00:48:43.901 --> 00:48:46.449
of temperature?
Student: Same.

00:48:46.449 --> 00:48:48.449
Professor Ramamurti
Shankar: Same.

00:48:48.449 --> 00:48:50.545
Because the internal energy
